title: #92Noon - The Kobe Kovenant
description: The entire Monday show is stream of consciousness on the tragic news related to the helicopter crash & deaths of all 9 aboard, including Kobe Bryant and his teenage daughter Gigi. Trent Tucker in studio for additional opinions during the final hour.
